==========
All type sections
==========
SECTION "ROM0 Data", ROM0
SECTION "ROMX Data", ROMX
SECTION "VRAM Data", VRAM
SECTION "SRAM Data", SRAM
SECTION "WRAM0 Data", WRAM0
SECTION "WRAMX Data", WRAMX
SECTION "OAM Data", OAM
SECTION "HRAM Data", HRAM
